description: Don Byron with Todd Marcus at the 2013 Mid Atlantic Jazz Festival. This segment was part of an hour long interview/workshop after a performance at the festival by the Todd Marcus Quintet featuring Don Byron. Recorded 2/16/13 by Blue House Productions.
fulltitle: Don Byron on audience response to his varied work (part 5 of 11)
